<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/satvir-kaur> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Satvir Kaur was appointed Parliamentary Secretary in the Cabinet Office on 7 September 2025. She was elected as the MP for Southampton Test in July 2024. Satvir Kaur was on maternity leave from 7 September 2025 until 22 February 2026, with a phased return from January 2026."@en .
